1. New Update Triggered From Cloud
   Server → Sends FCM Message (notification + data)

2. App Receives Cloud Message
   FirebaseMessagingService → Builds Notification

3. User Sees Notification With 2 Buttons
   [ACCEPT]   [REJECT]

4. User Taps a Button
   Button → Sends Action to BroadcastReceiver

5. Action Is Processed
   ACCEPT → Start Activity / Background Task
   REJECT → Stop / Ignore Request

6. App Handles Final Result
   Activity / Service runs with action = ACCEPT or REJECT
